{"tid":103981,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"內向撚應該一車車送去堆填區","createTime":"2017-02-01T17:51:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-02T12:54:55.000Z","uid":39812,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cb261350bf1dc4daa0ab07caed2dd87f4a051c0a","tid":103981,"uid":39812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T17:51:16.000Z","msg":"唔識表達自己，唔識行入人群<br />\n由幼稚園開始已經加重對呢個社會嘅負擔<br />\n外向撚由於夠social夠charm，凝聚倒其他人一齊工作以及消費<br />\n而內向撚因為缺乏人際網絡，工作上無法接軌<br />\n亦無法籍人際網絡提高生產力<br />\n缺乏社交圏子即係會少出街，少出街即係比外向撚嘅消費力低<br />\n因此為咗整個社會著想，根據物競天擇適者生存，送晒內向撚去堆填區留低外向撚嘅基因係對人類十分好嘅做法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：喺環保大道畀人送緊入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2899b38dddc9f3bb5b5d3c317b8c1f59f2e9e567","tid":103981,"uid":66769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T17:52:02.000Z","msg":"我要上車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dfcb268d680d8c7ed8211fc972f5dd89003543f","tid":103981,"uid":68823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T17:54:16.000Z","msg":"送埋我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee50c6e6d88095ea55cd0e4bd879b1a4192b0866","tid":103981,"uid":39323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T12:53:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7443e8927affb3eb789f7a71764cfe87496c775","tid":103981,"uid":7278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T12:54:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}